pageContext.claim: “The other night in North Carolina, two weeks ago, we won two Congressional races. They thought we'd lose one or the other was going to be maybe a one point, two point victory. We absolutely won them by so much nobody ever saw. I did something like this the night before the election.”
pageContext.analysis: Both seats were already held by Republicans, only one race was considered close, and the GOP candidate was ahead in every poll.
